      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "the difference between <i>emptyList()</i> and <i>EMPTY_LIST</i>: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/14870819/what-is-the-difference-between-collections-emptylist-and-collections-empty-lis?rq=1\" title=\"what is the difference between collections emptylist and collections empty lis\">stackoverflow.com/questions/14870819/&hellip;</a>"
