      "comment_id" : 48635810,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Starting with Java 7, you can let the compiler infer the type parameter of the generic method invocation from the target type: <code>List&lt;Foo&gt; list = Collections.emptyList()</code>"
    } ],
    "owner" : {
