    "question_id" : 5552258,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Starting with Java 5.0 you can specify the type of element in the container:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Collections.&lt;Foo&gt;emptyList()\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>I concur with the other responses that for cases where you want to return an empty list that stays empty, you should use this approach.</p>\n"
